ee.ria.dhx.types

Class DhxOrganisation

  • java.lang.Object
    • ee.ria.dhx.types.DhxOrganisation

  • public class DhxOrganisation
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents document sender or recipient organisation. Helps to easily define to whom or from who the document is really sent. Recipient might be not obvious if document is sent to representee. This class contains representees data if document is sent to/from representee and direct reciever data if it is sent directly, not to/from representee.
    Author:
    Aleksei Kokarev
